KwaZulu-Natal Premier Sihle Zikalala will deliver his State of the Province Address. PIETERMARITZBURG - KwaZulu-Natal Premier Sihle Zikalala delivers his state of the province address. This is against the backdrop of the July unrest that left the province’s business sector vulnerable and thousands of people jobless. READ: KZN premier says there will be zero tolerance for criminality The province is also suffering from an increase in service delivery protests and deepening poverty. The state of the province address takes place at the Royal Showgrounds in Pietermaritzburg.